{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839210656,"sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","part":{"id":"prt_d7843ec640013QXzn7h5tqGU2l","messageID":"msg_d7843d0e8001F2DbtK949WoI0i","sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-1ab99013853a4c94bd09a2ab2be9c356","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n2: \n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n5: \n6: ## Purpose\n7: \n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n11: \n12: ## Tech Stack\n13: \n14: | Layer | Technology |\n15: |-------|-----------|\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\n24: \n25: ## Architecture\n26: \n27: ```\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n34:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n36:   Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Conventions\n40: \n41: - Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n42: - Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-python/`\n43: - JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n44: - K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n45: - Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n\n## Purpose\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/project.md","time":{"start":1775839210636,"end":1775839210654}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839210662,"sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","part":{"id":"prt_d7843e07b001nubVWegh44VYhm","messageID":"msg_d7843d0e8001F2DbtK949WoI0i","sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-53b07f5fc7564414a3e679e8ee006e3e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n16: - `AgentRuntime` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n17: - `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n18: - `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n19: - `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n20: - 相关常量、标签、注解定义\n21: \n22: ## Out of Scope\n23: \n24: - Controller 实现\n25: - Webhook 验证逻辑\n26: - CRD YAML 生成\n27: - client-go 代码生成\n28: \n29: ## Dependencies\n30: \n31: 无外部依赖。\n32: \n33: ## Deliverables\n34: \n35: | File | Description |\n36: |------|-------------|\n37: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go` | AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n38: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n39: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Scheme 注册 |\n40: \n41: ## Acceptance Criteria\n42: \n43: - [ ] 类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n44: - [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n45: - [ ] 包含完整的字段注释\n46: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n47: \n48: ## References\n49: \n50: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n\n(End of file - total 50 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n- `AgentRuntime` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n- `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n- 相关常量、标签、注解定义","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","time":{"start":1775839210629,"end":1775839210661}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839210665,"sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","part":{"id":"prt_d7843e45a001hQgBRUneU1DKD5","messageID":"msg_d7843d0e8001F2DbtK949WoI0i","sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-6229108a88ea4668975b6333ef877015","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n22: - 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n23: - Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理运行时实例\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | PodSpec、EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements 等 |\n30: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n31: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n32: \n33: ### Controller-gen Markers\n34: \n35: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n36: |--------|------------|---------|\n37: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n38: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n39: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n40: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n41: | `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n42: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n43: \n44: ## Data Structures\n45: \n46: ### groupversion_info.go\n47: \n48: ```go\n49: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n50: package v1alpha1\n51: \n52: import \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n53: \n54: var (\n55:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n56:         Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n57:         Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n58:     }\n59:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n60:     AddToScheme   = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n61: )\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ### register.go\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: var (\n68:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n69:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n70:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n71:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n72: \n73:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n74:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n75:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n76: )\n77: \n78: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n79: \n80: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n81:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n82: }\n83: ```\n84: \n85: ### AgentRuntime Types\n86: \n87: ```go\n88: // +genclient\n89: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n90: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n91: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n92: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n93: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n94: type AgentRuntime struct {\n95:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n96:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n97:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n98:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n99: }\n100: \n101: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n102:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n103:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n104:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n105:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n106:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n107:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n108:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n109:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n110:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n111:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n112: }\n113: \n114: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n115:     // +optional\n116:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n117: }\n118: \n119: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n122:     // +optional\n123:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n124:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n125:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n126: }\n127: \n128: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n129: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n130: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n131:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n132:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n133:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n134: }\n135: ```\n136: \n137: ### CodeInterpreter Types\n138: \n139: ```go\n140: // +genclient\n141: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n142: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n143: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n144: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n145: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n146: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n147:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n148:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n149:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n150:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n151: }\n152: \n153: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n154:     // +optional\n155:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n156:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n157:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n158:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n159:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n160:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n161:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n162:     // +optional\n163:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n164:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n165:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n166:     // +optional\n167:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n168: }\n169: \n170: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n171:     // +optional\n172:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n173:     // +optional\n174:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n175: }\n176: \n177: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n178:     // +optional\n179:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n180:     // +optional\n181:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n182:     // +optional\n183:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n184:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n185:     // +optional\n186:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n187:     // +optional\n188:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n189:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n190:     // +listType=map\n191:     // +listMapKey=name\n192:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n193:     // +optional\n194:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n195:     // +optional\n196:     // +listType=atomic\n197:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n198:     // +optional\n199:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n200:     // +optional\n201:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n202: }\n203: \n204: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n205: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n206: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n207:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n208:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n209:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n210: }\n211: ```\n212: \n213: ### Shared Types\n214: \n215: ```go\n216: type TargetPort struct {\n217:     // +optional\n218:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n219:     // +optional\n220:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n221:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n222:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n223:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n224:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n225: }\n226: \n227: type AuthModeType string\n228: \n229: const (\n230:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n231:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n232: )\n233: \n234: type ProtocolType string\n235: \n236: const (\n237:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n238:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n239: )\n240: ```\n241: \n242: ## API Schema\n243: \n244: ### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n245: \n246: | Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n247: |----------|----------------------|\n248: | AgentRuntime | `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration` |\n249: | CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n250: \n251: ### Defaults\n252: \n253: | Field | Default Value |\n254: |-------|---------------|\n255: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n256: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n257: | `authMode` | `picod` |\n258: | `targetPort[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n259: \n260: ### Enums\n261: \n262: | Field | Allowed Values |\n263: |-------|----------------|\n264: | `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n265: | `protocol` | `HTTP`, `HTTPS` |\n266: \n267: ### REST Resource Plurals\n268: \n269: | Kind | Plural |\n270: |------|--------|\n271: | AgentRuntime | `agentruntimes` |\n272: | CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n273: \n274: ### Printer Columns\n275: \n276: | Name | Type | JSONPath |\n277: |------|------|----------|\n278: | Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n279: \n280: ## Error Handling\n281: \n282: - 无 spec 必填字段时，API server 拒绝创建请求（validation error）\n283: - 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n284: - Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n285: \n286: ## Testing Strategy\n287: \n288: ### Unit Tests\n289: \n290: | Test Category | Coverage |\n291: |---------------|----------|\n292: | DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段（deep vs shallow） |\n293: | Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n294: | Enum validation | 测试所有允许值及无效值 |\n295: | JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n296: \n297: ### Integration Tests\n298: \n299: - CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n300: - Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n301: \n302: ### Test File Structure\n303: \n304: ```\n305: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n306:   types_test.go       — DeepCopy、默认值、JSON 序列化测试\n307: ```\n308: \n309: ### Test Utilities\n310: \n311: 使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/webhook` 进行 validation 测试（如需 webhook）。\n312: \n313: ## File Structure\n314: \n315: ```\n316: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n317:   groupversion_info.go   — GroupVersion 定义、SchemeBuilder\n318:   register.go            — Kind constants、Resource helper\n319:   agentruntime_types.go  — AgentRuntime、AgentRuntimeList、SandboxTemplate\n320:   codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、共享类型\n321:   doc.go                 — 包文档（可选）\n322: \n323: client-go/                — 由 make gen-client 生成\n324:   clientset/\n325:   informers/\n326:   listers/\n327: ```\n328: \n329: ## Generation Commands\n330: \n331: | Command | Output |\n332: |---------|--------|\n333: | `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML（`manifests/charts/base/crds/`） |\n334: | `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n335: | `make gen-all` | 以上全部 |\n336: \n337: ## Open Questions\n338: \n339: - [已解决] 默认值由 kubebuilder markers 定义\n340: - [已解决] Status 字段包含 `Conditions`（通用）和 `Ready`（CodeInterpreter）\n341: - 是否需要添加 additionalPrinterColumns（如 Ready 状态）？\n342: - 是否需要 webhook 进行更复杂验证？\n343: \n344: ## References\n345: \n346: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n347: - client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n348: - controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`\n\n(End of file - total 348 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nCRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775839210632,"end":1775839210663}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839210668,"sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","part":{"id":"prt_d7843e8fd001ljoLexlamiHqyc","messageID":"msg_d7843d0e8001F2DbtK949WoI0i","sessionID":"ses_287bc4725ffeYyDVPatJ9Fx5O2","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-084f349927854debb6a71c08fc6957ca","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Task Checklist\n16: \n17: ### Phase 1: Project Setup\n18: \n19: - [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n20: - [ ] **T1.2** Initialize Go module if not exists (`go.mod` with `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`)\n21: - [ ] **T1.3** Add required dependencies to `go.mod`:\n22:   - `k8s.io/api v0.32.0`\n23:   - `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.32.0`\n24:   - `k8s.io/code-generator v0.32.0`\n25: \n26: ### Phase 2: Core Type Definitions\n27: \n28: - [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n29:   - Add package documentation\n30:   - Add `+groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` marker\n31:   - Add `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n32: \n33: - [ ] **T2.2** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n34:   - Define `GroupVersion` variable with group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` and version `v1alpha1`\n35:   - Define `SchemeBuilder` and `AddToScheme` function\n36:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n37: \n38: - [ ] **T2.3** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n39:   - Define `AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeListKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`\n40:   - Define `CodeInterpreterKind`, `CodeInterpreterListKind`, `CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind`\n41:   - Define `SchemeGroupVersion` and `Resource()` helper function\n42:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T2.4** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n45:   - Define `TargetPort` struct with fields: `PathPrefix`, `Name`, `Port`, `Protocol`\n46:   - Define `AuthModeType` type alias and constants: `AuthModePicoD`, `AuthModeNone`\n47:   - Define `ProtocolType` type alias and constants: `ProtocolTypeHTTP`, `ProtocolTypeHTTPS`\n48:   - Add appropriate kubebuilder validation markers\n49:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n50: \n51: - [ ] **T2.5** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n52:   - Define `AgentRuntime` struct with markers:\n53:     - `+genclient`\n54:     - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n55:     - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n56:     - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n57:     - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`\n58:     - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n59:   - Define `AgentRuntimeSpec` with fields: `Ports`, `Template`, `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`\n60:   - Define `AgentRuntimeStatus` with field: `Conditions`\n61:   - Define `SandboxTemplate` struct with fields: `Labels`, `Annotations`, `Spec`\n62:   - Define `AgentRuntimeList` struct with appropriate markers\n63:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n64: \n65: - [ ] **T2.6** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n66:   - Define `CodeInterpreter` struct with markers:\n67:     - `+genclient`\n68:     - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n69:     - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n70:     - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n71:     - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`\n72:     - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n73:   - Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields: `Ports`, `Template`, `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`, `WarmPoolSize`, `AuthMode`\n74:   - Define `CodeInterpreterStatus` with fields: `Conditions`, `Ready`\n75:   - Define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` struct with all fields from design\n76:   - Define `CodeInterpreterList` struct with appropriate markers\n77:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n78: \n79: ### Phase 3: Code Generation\n80: \n81: - [ ] **T3.1** Run `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` to generate DeepCopy methods\n82:   - Verify: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` file created\n83:   - Verify: All types implement `runtime.Object` interface\n84: \n85: - [ ] **T3.2** Run `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`\n86:   - Verify: CRD YAML files generated for `agentruntimes` and `codeinterpreters`\n87: \n88: - [ ] **T3.3** Run `client-gen` to generate client-go code\n89:   - Output to `client-go/` directory\n90:   - Verify: `clientset/`, `informers/`, `listers/` directories created\n91: \n92: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n93: \n94: - [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n95:   - Test DeepCopy for `AgentRuntime` (verify deep copy of all fields)\n96:   - Test DeepCopy for `CodeInterpreter` (verify deep copy of all fields)\n97:   - Test default values applied correctly (`sessionTimeout=15m`, `maxSessionDuration=8h`, `authMode=picod`)\n98:   - Test enum validation for `AuthModeType` and `ProtocolType`\n99:   - Test JSON serialization/deserialization for all types\n100:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n101: \n102: ### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n103: \n104: - [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n105:   - Fix any issues reported\n106: \n107: - [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n108:   - Fix any linting issues\n109: \n110: - [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase for all struct fields\n111:   - Check: `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`\n112:   - Check: `pathPrefix`, `imagePullPolicy`, `imagePullSecrets`\n113: \n114: - [ ] **T5.4** Verify Kubernetes API conventions compliance\n115:   - All required fields have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n116:   - Optional fields have `+optional` marker\n117:   - Default values specified with `+kubebuilder:default=...`\n118: \n119: ### Phase 6: Documentation\n120: \n121: - [ ] **T6.1** Add godoc comments to all exported types and fields\n122: - [ ] **T6.2** Verify package-level documentation in `doc.go` describes the API group purpose\n123: \n124: ---\n125: \n126: ## Task Dependencies\n127: \n128: ```\n129: T1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3 → T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3 → T2.4 → T2.5 → T2.6\n130:                                                             ↓\n131:                                                           T3.1 → T3.2 → T3.3\n132:                                                                             ↓\n133:                                                                           T4.1\n134:                                                                             ↓\n135:                                                      T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3 → T5.4\n136:                                                                             ↓\n137:                                                                           T6.1 → T6.2\n138: ```\n139: \n140: ---\n141: \n142: ## Verification Commands\n143: \n144: | Task | Verification Command |\n145: |------|----------------------|\n146: | T1.3 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n147: | T2.1-T2.6 | `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n148: | T3.1 | `test -f pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n149: | T3.2 | `test -f manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` |\n150: | T3.3 | `test -d client-go/clientset` |\n151: | T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v -cover` |\n152: | T5.1 | `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n153: | T5.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## Acceptance Criteria\n158: \n159: - [ ] All types defined per design.md specification\n160: - [ ] JSON tags use camelCase\n161: - [ ] Complete field comments for all exported types\n162: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n163: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n164: - [ ] DeepCopy methods generated and functional\n165: - [ ] CRD YAML files generated successfully\n166: - [ ] client-go code generated successfully\n167: - [ ] Unit tests pass with >80% coverage\n168: \n169: ---\n170: \n171: ## Notes\n172: \n173: - Follow Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n174: - Use controller-tools v0.17.2 for code generation\n175: - Reference implementation path (if available): `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n(End of file - total 175 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- [ ] **T1.2** Initialize Go module if not exists (`go.mod` with `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775839210634,"end":1775839210665}}}}
